Finding no support, the chicks flipped at random.
And after 10 hours in the newborns there was a total atrophy of the instincts.
The chicks did not react to light or sound.
And the misfortune was that after four days they were just dying.
“And twice we got the chicks born, but then we left them because it was impossible to work with them there,” Vladimir Sychev comments on the failure of the experiment with the chicks in space.
