At that time he preferred to enjoy his executions and those of Mincy in the National Team.
I remember when we first beat the United States during the 1989 Pre-Olympic in Mexico.
Then came the 1990 World Cup, where we came fourth and it should have been bronze if not for that Canadian referee who made us repeat the final play a second time, Reyes said.
Is that group from the 1990 World Cup the best National Team you've ever seen?
He is among the best, just like the one that beat the Dream Team at the 2004 Olympics.
